msgid ""
"<1.so>Ah... Here you can see <2.se_co>Hyrule Castle<3.re_co> in\n"
"the distance. So this must be <4.se_co>north of\n"
"the castle<5.re_co>.\n"
"The south side of the castle is where\n"
"Castle Town used to be, but I don't\n"
"see any buildings here, which means...\n"
"<6.so>Yes, indeed, I'd say this is likely on the\n"
"north side, across the castle moat.\n"
"It should be <7.se_co>southeast<8.re_co> of this stable."
msgstr ""

